# Quick Linting Reference

## Commands
lint          → npm run lint           # Check for errors
lint:fix      → npm run lint:fix       # Auto-fix errors
format        → npm run format         # Format all files
format:check  → npm run format:check   # Check formatting
type-check    → npm run type-check     # TypeScript check
check-all     → npm run check-all      # Run all checks

## Documentation
LINTING_GUIDE.md          → Comprehensive guide with examples
LINTING_SETUP_SUMMARY.md  → Setup summary and status
SETUP_HOOKS.md            → Git hooks setup

## Configuration Files
eslint.config.js          → ESLint 9 flat config
.prettierrc.json          → Prettier settings
.vscode/settings.json     → VSCode settings

