## Quick Fixes
Floating promises     → Add 'await' or 'void' or '.catch()'
|| to ??             → Replace with nullish coalescing
Async without await  → Remove 'async' or add 'await'
console.log          → Use console.warn or console.error

See LINTING_GUIDE.md for detailed examples and solutions.

